PRIVACY POLICY for Fart Counter mobile app
This privacy policy governs your use of the software application Fart Counter (“Application”) for mobile devices that was created by AtheryDevelopment. The application lets you couter your daily farts. 
 
What information does the Application obtain and how is it used?
Application does not collect user data.

Does the Application collect precise real time location information of the device?
Application does not collect user location.
 
Do third parties see and/or have access to information obtained by the Application?
Application does not use third parties.

Contact us
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Application, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via email at athery.development@gmail.com.
